Class TrueOrFalseQuestion

java.lang.Object
ntnu.fullstacksuperteam.backend.model.Question
ntnu.fullstacksuperteam.backend.model.TrueOrFalseQuestion
@Entity public class TrueOrFalseQuestion extends Question
The TrueOrFalseQuestion class extends the Question class to specifically represent questions that are answered with a true or false response.
